
⚡ espanso ftw

## install espanso

https://espanso.org/install/

## install our shared espanso triggers

$ espanso install ccs-package --git git@github.com:ryandeussing/red-hat-css-package.git --external

## sync the package to get updates to our shared espanso triggers

$ espanso package update ccs-package

## search triggers

Mac: `option + space`
Linux: `alt + space`

## view the triggers locally

$ espanso path // copy the 'Config' path

$ code {config-path} // e.g. '/Users/user/Library/Preferences/espanso' or '/home/user/.config/espanso'

☝️  package.yml contains the shared triggers

## add a personal trigger for your espanso config


  - trigger: ":espanso"
    replace: code {config-path}

